<div id="review_530597438" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/530597438" />
    <a title="A Man Called Ove" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8676317-a-man-called-ove"><img alt="A Man Called Ove" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1333976381p2/8676317.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/530597438?book_show_action=true">Feb 08, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="A Man Called Ove" class="user" itemprop="url" name="A Man Called Ove" href="/user/show/8676317-a-man-called-ove">A Man Called Ove</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title=" " href="/book/show/17264670-our-moon-has-blood-clots-the-exodus-of-kashmiri-pandits">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8676317-a-man-called-ove?shelf=indian-history-after-1947">indian-history-after-1947</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer530597438" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16262393531712799749">A painful, personal saga of the wrongs repeatedly done against the Kashmiri Pandits in the Kashmir Valley. Be it 1947, be it the 1980s or earlier instances before 1947. Events that have been distorted by many, aided by the fact that Kashmir has a complex history. <br/><br/>Wrt secularism - In India whenever post-independence communals riots are mentioned, the worst riots (not riots actually, a planned ethnic cleansing) is NOT mentioned. If u adopt an apologetic , appeasing attitude, alongwith hiding the f</span>
  <span id="freeText16262393531712799749" style="display:none">A painful, personal saga of the wrongs repeatedly done against the Kashmiri Pandits in the Kashmir Valley. Be it 1947, be it the 1980s or earlier instances before 1947. Events that have been distorted by many, aided by the fact that Kashmir has a complex history. <br /><br />Wrt secularism - In India whenever post-independence communals riots are mentioned, the worst riots (not riots actually, a planned ethnic cleansing) is NOT mentioned. If u adopt an apologetic , appeasing attitude, alongwith hiding the facts, u are only going to deepen the sense of wrong victimisation in a community. Let everyone know the full facts, let everyone be aware, let people debate and then people will move towards harmony.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16262393531712799749" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


